Input:
#include <stdio.h>
int main()
{
    double number;
    scanf("%lf", &number);

    if (number <= 0.0)
    {
        if (number == 0.0)
            printf("The number is 0.");
        else
            printf("Negative number.");
    }
    else
        printf("Positive number.");
}

Output:
1
Positive Number.

-1
Negative Number. 

0
The number is 0.
